All of the factory functions you’ll call (e.g., `NvBlastExtAuthoringCreateFractureTool`, `NvBlastExtAuthoringCreateMeshOnlyTriangles`, etc.) live in **NvBlastExtAuthoring.h**. ([NVIDIA Omniverse][3])

